<abstract><t>The Metro Ethernet Forum (MEF) has defined a rooted-multipoint Ethernet service known as Ethernet Tree (E-Tree).  [ETREE-FMWK] proposes a solution framework for supporting this service in MPLS networks. This document discusses how those functional requirements can be easily met with E-VPN.</t></abstract>

